research_municipality_step.notes: The City of Winona, TX operates under an Aldermanic form of government, electing five Aldermen and a Mayor to serve two-year terms. The information is based on the official City of Winona website and the Texas Municipal League directory. An older city council meeting agenda from April 2024 listed different aldermen (Craig Attaway and Laney Barnes) and a vacant alderman position, but the more recent sources (City website and TML directory) provide the listed officials.
